            <img src="/lib/images/Office 1.jpeg" alt="Large Paintings"> <!-- Image files which are located in a www.root folder, along with an alternative text which will show up if the image is unable to be displayed. -->
            </a>
        <h2 class="Column-Heading">Contact Us</h2>

        </div>
    </div>

</div>
